div.signin
  span.signin-copy
    | Island Â© 2012
  div.signin-bg
    img(src="https://d271mvlc6gc7bl.cloudfront.net/main/img/is-signin_bg_lo.jpg")
  div.signin-logo
    div
      img(src="https://d271mvlc6gc7bl.cloudfront.net/main/gfx/is-signin_lg_archs.png")
      img(src="https://d271mvlc6gc7bl.cloudfront.net/main/gfx/is-signin_lg.png")
  div.signin-action
    div.signin-spinner
    div.signin-strategies
      a.button.signin-strategy-btn(href='/auth/facebook') Connect with Facebook
      span.signin-or - or -
      a.button.signin-strategy-btn(href='/auth/twitter') Connect with Twitter
    div.signin-controls
      p#goto-register-form
        span You don't want to use Facebook or Twitter? 
        a(href='javascript:;', title='Sign up', style='font-weight:bold;') Sign up &rarr;
      p#goto-login-form(style='display: none')
        a(href='javascript:;', title='Log in', style='font-weight:bold;') &larr; Log in
    div.signin-forms
      form#login-form(method='post', action='/login')
        table
          tbody
            tr
              td
                input(name='username', type='text', placeholder='email')
              td
                input(name='password', type='password', placeholder='password')
              td
                input#login.is-button(type='submit', title='Log in', value='Log in')
      form#register-form(method='post', action='/signup')
        table
          tbody
            tr
              td
                input(name='newname', type='text', placeholder='your name')
              td
                input(name='newusername', type='text', placeholder='your email')
              td
                input(name='newpassword', type='password', placeholder='password')
              td
                input#add-member.is-button(type='submit', title='Sign up', value='Sign up')
  div.signin-quote
    p
      | &ldquo;The chance to directly connect with like minded individuals gives us an enormous outlet, a chance to create opportunities, to bridge greater gaps. We are doing this for our community, which includes ourselves. We hope to connect and relate lives, individually and communally, to become a movement, a force of energy, an embodiment of all the passion on our planet, in one place. Welcome to the Island.&rdquo;
      br
      br
      span(style="float: right;") -David Graham


